metadata.name: Patriotismo en reflejo (Patriotism in reflection) #1/20
metadata.description:
This is a digital copy edition of the selected physical artwork of Hernan Pazos.  Original artwork in oil on canvas (125cm x 170cm).  There are only 20 copies in this edition.  
All rights are reserved and terms and conditions for the digital collectible can be find under the unlockable content of this NFT under terms and condition.  Please, log in at qoriproject.io
